  "detailed_description": "<h1>EA SPORTS™ WRC 24</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849250/extras/eee14808112a98ea9e1a1daef778fe2f.avif?t=1748913259\" width=622 height=470 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849250/extras/3c559ea47049bfeac192a5e949fbfa2b.avif?t=1748913259\" width=622 height=1196 /></span><br><br>Buy EA SPORTS™ WRC 24* to get:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>EA SPORTS WRC<br></li><li>Locations & Cars Content Pack<br></li><li>Le Maestros Content Pack<br></li><li>Hard Chargers Content Pack</li></ul>Elevate your rally experience with the WRC 2024 Season Expansion. Discover thrilling new locations, Tet Rally Latvia and the Orlen 80th Rally Poland. Drive the latest high-performance vehicles, including the Ford Fiesta Rally3 Evo and Toyota GR Yaris Rally1 HYBRID '24. Customize your rally cars with more than 50 new liveries and compete against 52 official crews. Buckle up and get ready to embark on your rally journey.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Build the car of your dreams in our biggest rally game ever, EA SPORTS™ WRC, the all-new official videogame of the FIA World Rally Championship, the first developed by the award-winning team behind the DiRT Rally series.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849250/extras/0f0156d216724eb708955964128709f1.avif?t=1748913259\" width=610 height=3780 /></span>",
